                "ability_type_abbrev": "Su",
                "text": "Whenever the tattoo guardian\u2019s wearer takes damage, half of the damage is transferred to the guardian (as <i>shield other</i>). Additionally, the tattoo guardian gains a +2 bonus on attack and damage rolls against any creatures that damaged its wearer in the previous round."
