                "name": "Fluid Form",
                "ability_type": "Supernatural",
                "ability_type_abbrev": "Su",
                "text": "A tattoo guardian does not provoke attacks of opportunity because of movement. It is immune to critical hits and sneak attacks, and it cannot be knocked prone or grappled."
            },
